title: Drawing, "Female Head, Front, Eyes Closed"
description: In this view, the full face is squared off at the chin; the heavy eyebrows slant upward; the nose is comprised of a curved vertical line and a wavy horizontal line and shading depicting the nostrils; and the lips are full and closed. Curly, shoulder length hair divides at a center part. Faint lines framing the hair may represent a headdress.
